data.description: Professional pictures coming soon!! By appointment only please do not bother current tenants! Rented out until the first week of April. Fully furnished and ready to move in. Furniture optional. Gorgeous 2bd/1ba single family home in the heart of Lighthouse Point. Look no further because this home is in the best location! Less than 3 miles from Deerfield Beach, restaurants and shopping. It is also very close to Pompano Beach. Lots of natural light throughout the home. The comfy Florida room is a beachcomber's delight. Relax on the patio after a day at the beach! Very large backyard with room for a pool. New water heater. New electrical. New AC. Hurricane rated shed. Don't miss out on this amazing home!!
